Center can be handy (tons of mass dept.  chain stores), but the shops aren鈥檛 great  the exterior is hideous. Cute hotel gift shop that stocks wonderful things like Marvis toothpaste alongside novelties like Mile High kits!Lastly, this is LA. Every hotel has a fun pool scene, strong restaurant  fun bar 鈥?EXCEPT the Sofitel. If you like to mix business  pleasure, plan on having to head out to other hotels (or nightlife destinations). 
